snippet.title: Linus Tech Tips
snippet.description:
Looking for a Tech YouTuber?

Linus Tech Tips is a passionate team of "professionally curious" experts in consumer technology and video production which aims to inform and educate people of all ages through our entertaining videos. We create product reviews, step-by-step computer build guides, and a variety of other tech-focused content.

Schedule:
New videos every Saturday to Thursday @ 10:00am Pacific
Live WAN Show podcasts every Friday @ ~5:00pm Pacific
